        <Parent_String>woodworking [300054083], woodworking and woodworking processes and techniques [300155056], processes and techniques by material [300053900], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
