    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The art of building with wood, especially in the construction of buildings and other structures, including the installation of floors, windows, and other trim work. For the making of fine furniture and intricate woodwork, see "cabinetmaking." For the broader activity of working in wood more generally, use "woodworking."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
